Directory structure
===============
- test/ : test cases
- parser/ : parser
- fides/ : fides headers and perl generators -- requires Fides support 
- cesk/ : implementation of the CESK machine
- scesk/ : implementation of the 2/S CESK machine
- buildsrc/ : all files used to build the executable
- bin/ : the executable and binary spm's
- doc/ : documentation used to build the machine

Executing
==================
./ruse [-idfvwsc] sourcefile

Testing 
==================
./testruse

Specification
==================
language-spec
